2. `Docs/04_BACKEND_SPEC.md` §8.4 — **K5**: çözümleme sırası (rating toplamı), `calculate_relevance_score` formülü + sabitler, kapsam kuralı
3. `Docs/01_DOMAIN_MODEL.md` §4 ProcessedItem — skor anlamı + `content_category` rating-tabanlı seçim
4. `services/processor/enricher.py` + `scorer.py` (mevcut) — wire edilecek yüzey

**Uygulama planı:**
1. `keyword_pool.py` — `count_matches_by_category` rating taşır; `category_score(cat) = Σ rating` (distinct keyword); `resolve_content_category(...) -> (category, all_matched, scored_for_winner)`: `all` → default_category; `filtered` → max rating-toplamı, eşitlik → default_category; hiç eşleşme → default_category (`Docs/04` §8.4 sırası 1–4)
2. `scorer.py` — sabitler `REL_COVERAGE_WEIGHT=0.7, REL_FREQ_WEIGHT=0.3, RATING_SATURATION=18.0, FREQ_NORMALIZE_CAP=3.0`; `calculate_relevance_score(content, scored)`: boş → 0.0; `coverage=min(Σrating/18,1)`; `freq=min(Σ(rating·hits)/(Σrating·3),1)`; `round(0.7·cov+0.3·freq,4)` (`Docs/04` §8.4 kod)
